OL,3,CGreen Party candidate caught removing
OL,4,CLabour leaflet from letterbox
OL,6,FA Wales Green Party candidate has been
OL,7,Fcaught on camera removing a Labour
OL,8,Fparty leaflet from a letterbox while
OL,9,Fout canvassing.
OL,11,FIn doorbell camera footage exclusively
OL,12,Fshared with ITV News, Rob James can be
OL,13,Fseen posting his party's own leaflet
OL,14,Fthrough the door while then removing
OL,15,Fone posted by Labour's Martyn
OL,16,FPalfreman just moments earlier.
OL,18,FMr James is a former Labour group
OL,19,Fleader on Carmarthenshire County
OL,20,FCouncil. He left the party to join the
OL,21,FGreens in November 2025.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
