OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776974758
OL,3,CGreen Party candidate caught removing
OL,4,CLabour leaflet from letterbox
OL,6,FBoth he and Mr Palfreman are
OL,7,Fcandidates standing in the
OL,8,Fconstituency of Sir Gaerfyrddin for
OL,9,FMay's Senedd Election. A full list of
OL,10,Fcandidates standing in the
OL,11,Fconstituency can be found here.
OL,13,FAfter being alerted to the footage,
OL,14,Fthe Wales Green Party said it had
OL,15,Fspoken to Mr James about the incident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
