OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776974758
OL,3,CGreen Party candidate caught removing
OL,4,CLabour leaflet from letterbox
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the party said: "We
OL,7,Fhave reviewed the footage and have
OL,8,Fspoken to the candidate to make clear
OL,9,Fthat removing other party leaflets
OL,10,Fisn't acceptable. He acknowledges he
OL,11,Fshould not have removed the leaflet."
OL,13,FWelsh Labour said it was
OL,14,F"disappointing" to see parties
OL,15,Femploying "unfair tactics".
OL,17,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"Our candidates and volunteers are out
OL,19,Fevery day, knocking on doors,
OL,20,Fdelivering leaflets, working hard to
OL,21,Fget our message out there.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
