CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776974758
OL,3,CGreen Party candidate caught removing
OL,4,CLabour leaflet from letterbox
OL,6,F"Welsh Labour is campaigning for a
OL,7,Ffairer future for all, so it's
OL,8,Fdisappointing to see other parties
OL,9,Fresorting to unfair tactics.
OL,11,F"The problem with the Greens is
OL,12,Fthey're not as cuddly as they make
OL,13,Fout. He probably didn't even recycle
OL,14,Fit."
OL,16,FPlaid Cymru and Reform have also been
OL,17,Fapproached for comment.
